+Network issues are often temporary. Try again in a few minutes.
+
+### Option 4: Check VPN/Firewall
+- Disconnect VPN if connected
+- Check firewall settings
+- Contact network admin if on corporate network
+
+## Recommended Next Steps
+
+1. **Try SSH first** (most reliable):
+   ```bash
+   git remote set-url origin git@github.com:Stranger-Siv/Kaam247.git
+   git push
+   ```
+
+2. **If SSH doesn't work**, try:
+   ```bash
+   git config --global http.timeout 300
+   git push
+   ```
+
+3. **If still failing**, check network/VPN/firewall settings
